Package: divaodv
Title: ODV-Style Oceanographic Section Plots via DIVAnd Interpolation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ilia", "Maidanik", , "imaidanik@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6886-4225"))
Description: Generates publication-quality Ocean Data View (ODV) style
    depth-time section plots for oceanographic profile data. Uses the
    DIVAnd (Data-Interpolating Variational Analysis) algorithm via Julia
    to interpolate scattered observations onto a regular grid, then
    renders filled-contour sections with ggplot2 and metR. Supports
    configurable correlation lengths, signal-to-noise parameters, log
    transforms for biological/chemical variables, and multiple colour
    palettes including the classic ODV rainbow.
